==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Subderivative
<hw>Sub`de*riv"a*tive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A word
derived from a derivative, and not directly from the root; <as>as,
⟦ldquo⟧friendliness⟦rdquo⟧ is a <ex>subderivative</ex>, being derived
from ⟦ldquo⟧friendly⟦rdquo⟧, which is in turn a derivative from
⟦ldquo⟧friend.⟦rdquo⟧</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Subdiaconate</ent>⟦br⟧
